|   + HOW TO INSTALL                                                           |
|     - copy "config.TEMPLATE.php" to "config.php" and set your info           |
|     - run "utils/getData.php"                                                |
|     - [optional*] run "utils/getFlags.php"                                   |
|     - [optional*] run "utils/getImages.php"                                  |
|     - run "utils/addToDb.php"                                                |
|     - that _should_ be all                                                   |
|                                                                              |
| * by optional I actually mean highly recommended :)                          |
